First we need the ActiveMQ core jar. 

Our @BuildConfig.groovy@ looks something like...

{code}
grails.project.dependency.resolution = {
    inherits "global"
    log "warn"
    repositories {
        grailsHome()
        mavenCentral()
    }  
    dependencies {
        compile 'org.apache.activemq:activemq-core:5.3.0'
    }
}
{code}

